title: Top Less
description:
From Tadanohito:

This collection has: Humiliation one-shot set at an office, pleasant school one-shot, blackmail and humiliation series set at an office (with old guys), crazy-humorous series about a maid and the family she works for. Quite a wide variety. Light censorship.

1. Undominance
2. Topless
3. 7th Period -Two Confessions of Love-
4-6. After 5
7. Invitation into the Nokogiri Household
8. Retaliation of the Nokogiri Household
9. Return of the Nokogiri Household
10. Intrigue in the Nokogiri Household
